{"tid":691872,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"楊千嬅丁子高為《超人特工隊2》配音　網民一面倒插爆","createTime":"2018-06-06T06:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T15:59:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":11,"dislike":196,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e7eea09b4cd802c2bf0709a4f5d792a297879a","tid":691872,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:22:49.000Z","msg":"文：Hin<br />\n<br />\n迪士尼動畫《超人特工隊》（The Incredibles）自2004年上映後，不少人都期待續集的面世，相隔14年後今年終傳來好消息，《超人特工隊2》（Incredibles 2）將於今年7月在香港上映！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/15/87/10158749_733341.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F15%2F87%2F10158749_733341.jpg&h=1cfd048f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊千嬅及老公丁子高為《超人特工隊2》配音（Facebook圖片）<br />\n<br />\n今日（5號）官方宣布《超人特工隊2》邀請到歌楊千嬅及老公丁子高為香港版配音，分別聲演「彈弓女俠」及「超能先生」。首度以夫妻檔上陣配音，楊千嬅笑言適逢兒子Torres 6歲生日，故此就當送給他一份驚喜生日禮物，而丁子高則指兩夫妻合作配音是機會難逢，加上由故事到角色都適合二人，故此答應聲演，盼為兒子帶來最美好的回憶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/15/87/10158750_175856.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F15%2F87%2F10158750_175856.jpg&h=6aef4a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢對真．夫婦連配音都做夫婦（Facebook圖片）<br />\n<br />\n然而楊千嬅及丁子高聲演英雄夫婦的消息一出後，大批網民分別在社交網及討論區表達不滿，皆因當年《超人特工隊》的「超能先生」和「彈弓女俠」分別由吳鎮宇及郭藹明聲演，故此不少人希望第二集由原班人馬繼績聲演：「還我吳鎮宇郭藹明。」、「對佢哋冇偏見，但係呢個係電影連貫問題，配音唔同咗點樣入戲！」、「冇人想要新配音。」甚至有網民直言睇英文版也不會看配音版。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/15/87/10158754_859956.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F15%2F87%2F10158754_859956.jpg&h=6ee542d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當年《超人特工隊》由吳鎮宇（右二）同郭藹明（左三）聲演英雄夫婦（視覺中國圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/15/87/10158752_821944.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F15%2F87%2F10158752_821944.jpg&h=d71a8dd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c74eda351641b69ef409b15ff03fb98b4c40287","tid":691872,"uid":31990,"like":136,"dislike":1,"score":135,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:24:51.000Z","msg":"小麗仲係咪鄭融先"},{"pid":"fdee1a50263889860d107dcea66a6f681d56bd87","tid":691872,"uid":113178,"like":322,"dislike":3,"score":319,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"唔用原本嘅配音會食唔到童年回憶呢條水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e813633b4ab7ae5f79501235f8438ee550251cc","tid":691872,"uid":58552,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:28:34.000Z","msg":"倒米"},{"pid":"b308d3cbddd976b57aabd3d31dc9505484c1fcda","tid":691872,"uid":13504,"like":354,"dislike":23,"score":331,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:36:20.000Z","msg":"楊千嬅都真係唔知邊方面叻，無樣無身材無唱功無演技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293e2adf86c6718ce75f9a5e63b266456fde51cc","tid":691872,"uid":81562,"like":307,"dislike":5,"score":302,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:36:23.000Z","msg":"楊千嬅把聲咁八婆 丁子高把聲邊岩大隻佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要夫妻檔就索性劉青雲郭藹明啦 而家搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecbbef7be6c9e247ec0264c1c97662e9eab300c1","tid":691872,"uid":119450,"like":169,"dislike":1,"score":168,"quote":{"pid":"fdee1a50263889860d107dcea66a6f681d56bd87","tid":691872,"uid":113178,"like":322,"dislike":3,"score":319,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"唔用原本嘅配音會食唔到童年回憶呢條水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:39:21.000Z","msg":"當年呢套戲中文配音出名過英文<br />\n就好似怪獸公司司大眼仔米高一樣<br />\n所以我同意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4190cfd28935cd2b7e2c6c82b8cd90ff66c0483","tid":691872,"uid":67500,"like":4,"dislike":115,"score":-111,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:49:38.